data.description: Love a good single story? This home is located in the desirable Lakes gated community of Discovery Bay! Mosaic Residence 2. Elegant floor plan with an abundance of natural light throughout. This model offers a formal living room upon entering that can be used for a dining room or play room, office or whatever you choose. Entry then leads to a large family room adorned with a ship lap feature wall and sits adjacent to the kitchen & spacious dining area.  Gourmet kitchen offers granite counters, upgraded cabinetry, and a massive island! A gas stove, built in oven, and pantry too.  Bright and airy primary suite with private bath and walk-in closet. 3 additional bedrooms including a Jr Suite, which is ideal for company. Landscaped backyard with newer pavers and cement side yard, California Sun Room with a fireplace. Low maintenance yard with drought tolerant plants. Gated community with greenbelt, lakes, walking paths and playgrounds. Close to schools and shopping. Home lies in boundaries of Old River school. Visit us today and buy before the end of 2023~
